
. parameterless macros: @logreturn = @log @diff
. parameterized macros: @macr(a,b) = @log @func(a) @mean(axis=b)
. enable personal loaddata functions
. enable command line properties: -Dproperty=bla (property = "bla"), -Dproperty (property = 1)
. call of not defined properties raises exception
. properties can be declared in .pypusrc [properties] section
